title: Brand New Studio Available for Rent
posting_body: ['NEW RENTAL LISTING!', 'Be the first to live in these unique industrial lofts in NE Minneapolis!', 'Units feature high ceilings and giant outdoor patios!', 'American Spirit Lofts - 22 lofts built on top of a warehouse that houses an indoor soccer field, boxing gym, coffee shop and lounge area.', 'Right next to Crossfit Minneapolis and Minneapolis Cider Company in an up and coming area.', 'Close proximity to downtown and easy access to 35W!', 'PHOTOS MAY BE OF SIMILAR OR MODEL UNIT.', 'Building/Unit: American Spirit Lofts #4', 'Price: $1,350', 'Available:', '9/15', 'Bedrooms: 0', 'Full Bathrooms: 1', 'Parking: Garage', 'Pets: Cats okay and Dogs', 'okay', 'Application fee: $78', 'Square Footage: 470', "Deposit: One month's rent", 'Vlad Istrate | Leasing Agent | DRG', 'show contact info', 'Listed by DRG.', 'Equal housing broker.', 'Tags: Condo, Rental, Condo Rental, Apartment, Apartment Rental, One Bed Rental, Two Bed Rental, Three Bed Rental, Pet Friendly Rental, Luxury, Luxury Rental, Luxury Apartment, North Loop, North Loop Rental, Mill District, Mill District Rental, Uptown, Uptown Rental, Northeast, Northeast Rental, North Loop Apartment, North Loop Condo, Uptown Apartment, Uptown Condo, Northeast Apartment, Northeast Condo.']
